%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20top%20New%20York%20official%20was%20paid%20off%20by%20China%20with%20salted%20ducks%2C%20a%20job%20for%20her%20cousin%2C%20and%20millions%20to%20her%20husband's%20business%3A%20DOJ%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Linda%20Sun%2C%20left%2C%20at%20the%20Brooklyn%20federal%20court.%20On%20the%20right%20are%20Nanjing-style%20salted%20ducks.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d7e6f714a5cd1fcc8cf7de%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELinda%20Sun%20was%20charged%20on%20Tuesday%20in%20Brooklyn%20by%20federal%20prosecutors%20with%20money%20laundering%2C%20visa%20fraud%2C%20and%20conspiracy%20to%20Violate%20the%20Foreign%20Agents%20Registration%20Act.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FCorey%20Sipkin%20and%20Zhang%20Peng%2FLightRocket%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20former%20top%20aide%20to%20New%20York's%20governor%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20secretly%20working%20for%20China.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EProsecutors%20say%20Linda%20Sun%20carried%20out%20tasks%20for%20Beijing%20like%20blocking%20Taiwan's%20access%20to%20authorities.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe's%20accused%20of%20receiving%20gifts%20in%20return%20like%20salted%20ducks%20and%20VIP%20suite%20access%20to%20sporting%20events.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFederal%20prosecutors%20have%20accused%20a%20former%20high-level%20aide%20to%20New%20York's%20governor%20of%20secretly%20working%20for%20China%20in%20exchange%20for%20perks%20like%20orchestra%20tickets%2C%20millions%20in%20cash%2C%20and%20over%20a%20dozen%20Nanjing-style%20salted%20ducks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELinda%20Sun%2C%20who%20worked%20for%20Gov.%20Kathy%20Hochul%20and%20her%20predecessor%2C%20Andrew%20Cuomo%2C%20was%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fusao-edny%2Fpr%2Fformer-high-ranking-new-york-state-government-employee-charged-acting-undisclosed%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echarged%20on%20Tuesday%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0with%20over%2010%20criminal%20counts%2C%20including%20visa%20fraud%2C%20money%20laundering%2C%20and%20conspiracy%20to%20violate%20the%20Foreign%20Agents%20Registration%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESun%2C%2040%2C%20is%20accused%20of%20blocking%20Taiwanese%20officials'%20access%20to%20the%20New%20York%20governor's%20office%20and%20changing%20public%20messages%20from%20both%20governors%20to%20boost%20China's%20talking%20points%2C%20among%20other%20acts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Justice%20Department%2C%20she%20also%20sent%20messages%20informing%20the%20Chinese%20consulate%20about%20Taiwan's%20requests%20to%20the%20governor's%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20all%20been%20taken%20of%20satisfactorily%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20is%20alleged%20to%20written%20in%20a%20message%20to%20a%20Chinese%20official%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20an%20FYI%2C%20I%20already%20blocked%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20also%20wrote%20in%202019%20when%20the%20office%20of%20Taiwan's%20president%20invited%20Cuomo%20to%20a%20banquet%2C%20per%20prosecutors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECourt%20filings%20unsealed%20on%20Tuesday%20said%20that%20Sun%20held%20several%20high-level%20positions%20while%20working%20for%20over%20a%20decade%20in%20the%20New%20York%20government%2C%20including%20as%20director%20for%20Asian-American%20affairs%20and%20Queens%20regional%20representative%20under%20Cuomo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20promoted%20to%20deputy%20chief%20of%20staff%20under%20Hochul%20in%20September%202021%2C%20and%20went%20on%20to%20become%20deputy%20commissioner%20for%20strategic%20business%20development%20in%20the%20New%20York%20Labor%20Department%20from%20September%202022%20to%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20said%20that%20during%20this%20time%2C%20Sun%20would%20use%20bogus%20invitation%20letters%20to%20set%20up%20meetings%20for%20Chinese%20officials%20with%20New%20York%20authorities.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20she%20also%20tried%20to%20organize%20a%20trip%20to%20China%20for%20Hochul%2C%20per%20court%20filings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSun%20wielded%20her%20position%20of%20influence%20among%20executives%20to%20covertly%20promote%20PRC%20and%20CCP%20agendas%2C%20directly%20threatening%20our%20country's%20national%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20FBI%20Acting%20Assistant%20Director%20Curtis%2C%20referring%20to%20China's%20official%20name%20and%20the%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22052df450-e07a-4818-9140-f6359655ee18%5C%22%3EDucks%2C%20VIP%20suite%20access%2C%20and%20a%20condo%20in%20Honolulu%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20return%2C%20Sun%20received%20a%20slew%20of%20undeclared%20gifts%2C%20including%20ballet%20and%20orchestra%20tickets%2C%20VIP%20suite%20access%20at%20sporting%20events%2C%20promotion%20for%20a%20friend's%20company%2C%20and%20millions%20of%20dollars%20to%20the%20China-based%20business%20of%20her%20husband%2C%20Chris%20Hu%2C%20per%20court%20filings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestigators%20said%20Sun%20also%20received%20salted%20ducks%20prepared%20by%20the%20personal%20chef%20of%20an%20official%20at%20the%20Chinese%20consulate%2C%20receiving%20them%20on%20four%20occasions%20from%202021%20to%202022.%20Court%20documents%20say%20she%20got%20up%20to%20six%20ducks%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFederal%20prosecutors%20added%20that%20Sun%20was%20also%20rewarded%20with%20a%20job%20for%20her%20cousin%20in%20China%20and%20received%20benefits%20from%20local%20officials%20when%20traveling%20with%20a%20colleague%20for%20a%20work%20trip%20to%20Jiangsu%20province.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPer%20the%20Justice%20Department%2C%20Sun%20and%20Hu%20used%20the%20money%20they%20received%20from%20Chinese%20officials%20to%20buy%20at%20least%20two%20properties%20%E2%80%94%20one%20in%20Manhasset%2C%20New%20York%2C%20that's%20now%20worth%20%244.1%20million%2C%20and%20a%20condominium%20in%20Honolulu%2C%20worth%20%242.1%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20bought%20luxury%20cars%20like%20a%202024%20Ferrari%2C%20the%20officials%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHu%20has%20been%20charged%20by%20the%20Justice%20Department%20too%2C%20and%20is%20accused%20of%20laundering%20money%20and%20opening%20bank%20accounts%20with%20a%20relative's%20driver's%20license%20photo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Hochul%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20New%20York%20governor's%20office%20hired%20Sun%20more%20than%2010%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20terminated%20her%20employment%20in%20March%202023%20after%20discovering%20evidence%20of%20misconduct%2C%20immediately%20reported%20her%20actions%20to%20law%20enforcement%2C%20and%20have%20assisted%20law%20enforcement%20throughout%20this%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Hochul%20was%20asked%20on%20Tuesday%20about%20Sun%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fgovkathyhochul%2Fgovernor-hochul-is-a-guest-on-wnycs-all-things-considered%3Fsi%3D6d175bc91f1f4c99ad6237bcfc46801e%26utm_source%3Dclipboard%26utm_medium%3Dtext%26utm_campaign%3Dsocial_sharing%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWNYC's%20radio%20podcast%20%26quot%3BAll%20Things%20Considered%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20governor%20said%20that%20the%20aide%20was%20fired%20%26quot%3Bthe%20second%20we%20discovered%20some%20levels%20of%20misconduct.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20declined%20to%20say%20which%20of%20Sun's%20behaviors%20were%20flagged%20by%20her%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiu%20Pengyu%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Chinese%20embassy%20in%20Washington%2C%20told%20BI%20he%20was%20unaware%20of%20the%20specific%20details%20of%20Sun's%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20the%20US%20government%20and%20media%20have%20frequently%20hyped%20up%20the%20so-called%20'Chinese%20agents'%20narratives%2C%20many%20of%20which%20have%20later%20been%20proven%20untrue%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20embassy%20opposed%20%26quot%3Bthe%20groundlessly%20slandering%20and%20smearing%20targeting%20China.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJarrod%20Schaeffer%2C%20Sun's%20lawyer%2C%20told%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fformer-hochul-aide-arrested-new-york-c588a95e87b853ca3d23b36aae4c87cd%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAssociated%20Press%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday%3A%20%26quot%3BWe're%20looking%20forward%20to%20addressing%20these%20charges%20in%20court.%20Our%20client%20is%20understandably%20upset%20that%20these%20charges%20have%20been%20brought.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchaeffer%20and%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Cuomo%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours%20by%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flinda-sun-new-york-governor-top-aide-salted-ducks-china-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725428169000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d7e6f714a5cd1fcc8cf7de%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flinda-sun-new-york-governor-top-aide-salted-ducks-china-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Linda%20Sun%2C%2040%2C%20was%20charged%20on%20Tuesday%20with%2010%20criminal%20counts%2C%20with%20prosecutors%20saying%20she%20blocked%20Taiwan's%20access%20to%20New%20York%20governors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mloh%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Loh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flinda-sun-new-york-governor-top-aide-salted-ducks-china-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%20services%20sector%20growth%20surges%20to%205-month%20high%20in%20August%3A%20PMI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725428037000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2020-10%2F06%2Fthumb%2Ffeatu