ies-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edampened%20by%20stormy%20weather%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Participants%20shared%20stories%20of%20flooded%20tents%20and%20porta-potties%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDJ%20Diplo%20documented%20his%20journey%20leaving%20the%20event%20in%202023%2C%20walking%20six%20miles%20in%20mud%20to%20his%20private%20jet%20to%20then%20fly%20to%20Washington%2C%20DC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20exodus%20from%20the%20event%20has%20been%20documented%20to%20be%20notoriously%20slow%20and%20difficult.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20event's%20website%20states%20that%20because%20there%20is%20a%20fixed%20number%20of%20vehicles%20that%20can%20leave%20Black%20Rock%20City%20and%20get%20onto%20Country%20Route%2034%20per%20hour%2C%20exiting%20participants%20often%20face%20long%20waiting%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20press%20time%2C%20the%20annual%20exodus%20appeared%20to%20be%20back%20on%20track.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cspan%3EIt's%20taking%20about%2020%20minutes%20to%20exit%20Black%20Rock%20City.%20Exodus%20is%20continuing%20and%20conditions%20are%20great%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Burning%20Man%20Traffic%20X%20account%20posted%20on%20Tuesday%20night.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBurning%20Man's%20press%20team%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%2C%20sent%20outside%20business%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fburning-man-engulfed-dust-storm-that-snarled-exits-desert-camp-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725427820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ccd0cb1aa2ac29ee3465ab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fburning-man-engulfed-dust-storm-that-snarled-exits-desert-camp-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Burning%20Man's%20traffic%20account%20said%20those%20leaving%20the%20venue%20could%20expect%20a%20six-hour%20wait.%2