%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113050381%2Cimgsize-123366.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fscience%2Fwhy-is-everything-in-space-constantly-moving-the-role-of-the-big-bang-angular-momentum-and-dark-matter%2Farticleshow%2F113050287.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20article%20explores%20how%20the%20Big%20Bang%20initiated%20the%20universe's%20continuous%20motion%2C%20affecting%20vast%20cosmic%20distances%20through%20expansion.%20Angular%20momentum%20drives%20local%20rotations%2C%20while%20dark%20matter%20influences%20galaxy%20dynamics.%20The%20piece%20highlights%20that%20motion%20is%20a%20fundamental%20aspect%20of%20the%20universe%2C%20reflecting%20ongoing%20chemical%20and%20physical%20processes%20that%20require%20energy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SCIENCE%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fscience%2Fwhy-is-everything-in-space-constantly-moving-the-role-of-the-big-bang-angular-momentum-and-dark-matter%2Farticleshow%2F113050287.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Modi%20Meets%20Brunei%20Sultan%20Today%20At%20Luxury%20Palace%3A%2010%20Points%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOn%20day%202%20of%20the%20tour%2C%20PM%20Modi%20met%C2%A0the%20Sultan%20of%20Brunei%2C%20Hassanal%20Bolkiah.The%20Sultan%20is%20the%20second-longest%20reigning%20monarch%20in%20the%20world%20after%20the%20late%20Queen%20Elizabeth%20II.%20With%20an%20estimated%20net%20worth%20of%20around%20%2430%20billion%2C%20he%20was%20once%20the%20world's%20richest%20person.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BDelighted%20to%20meet%20His%20Majesty%20Sultan%20Haji%20Hassanal%20Bolkiah.%20Our%20talks%20were%20wide%20ranging%20and%20included%20ways%20to%20further%20cement%20bilateral%20ties%20between%20our%20nations.%20We%20are%20going%20to%20further%20expand%20trade%20ties%2C%20commercial%20linkages%20and%20people-to-people%20exchanges%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20PM%20Modi%