efore%20bed%20rather%20than%20processing%20it%20in%20bed%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20breathing%20exercises%20before%20bed%20can%20help%20you%20sleep%20better.%20In%202020%2C%20BI%20reported%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Fbreathing-exercises-for-sleep%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethree%20breathing%20exercises%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20can%20promote%20better%20sleep%3A%20diaphragmatic%20breathing%2C%20body%20scan%2C%20and%20a%204-7-8%20breathing%20method.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20representative%20for%20Fallon%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%2C%20sent%20outside%20business%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjimmy-fallon-tapes-his-mouth-sleep-experts-warn-against-it-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725424200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d7d2f61d8d2deb96b87811%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjimmy-fallon-tapes-his-mouth-sleep-experts-warn-against-it-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI%20have%20to%20do%20this%20under%20supervision.%20So%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20have%20security%20guards%20next%20to%20my%20bed%20and%20try%20this%E2%80%94I'm%20not%20kidding!%26quot%3B%20the%20%26quot%3BTonight%20Show%26quot%3B%20host%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22eliam%40insider.com%20(Erin%20Liam)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjimmy-fallon-tapes-his-mouth-sleep-experts-warn-against-it-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20is%20Deepthi%20Jeevanji%3F%20Meet%20the%20world%20champion%20sprinter%20and%20Paris%20Paralympics%20400m%20(T20)%20medallist%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A172542407