0friend%20Shaik%20were%20returning%20after%20visiting%20his%20cousin%20in%20Dallas.%20Lokesh%20Palacharla%20was%20traveling%20to%20Bentonville%20to%20meet%20his%20wife.%20Dharshini%20Vasudevan%2C%20who%20had%20finished%20her%20Master's%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Texas%20and%20had%20been%20working%20in%20the%20US%2C%20was%20going%20to%20visit%20her%20uncle%20in%20Bentonville.%20They%20connected%20through%20a%20carpooling%20app%20and%20this%20helped%20authorities%20identify%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDarshini%20Vasudevan's%20father%20had%20tagged%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20in%20a%20Twitter%20post%20three%20days%20back%20and%20sought%20help%20in%20locating%20his%20daughter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDear%20Sir%2C%20My%20daughter%20Dharshini%20Vasudevan%20holding%20Indian%20passport%20No-T6215559%20have%20been%20in%20USA%20for%20the%20last%203%20years%2C%202%20years%20of%20MS%20studies%20and%20later%201%20year%20of%20Employment%20and%20stays%203150%20Avenue%20of%20the%20stars%20Apt%201110-Frisco%2CTexas-75034.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYesterday%20evening%20she%20took%20a%20car%20pooling%20along%20with%203%20others%20around%203pm%20till%204pm%20she%20was%20actively%20messaging%20and%20reachable%20on%20phone%20after%204pm%20no%20further%20contacts%20could%20be%20established%20with%20her%20as%20well%20other%203%20people%20who%20were%20travelling%20with%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20the%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOrampati's%20father%20Subhash%20Chandra%20Reddy%20owns%20a%20Hyderabad-based%20firm%20named%20Max%20Agri%20Genetics%20Private%20Limited.%20Aryan%20completed%20his%20engineering%20degree%20at%20Amrita%20Vishwa%20Vidyapeetham%20in%20Coimbatore.%20%26quot%3BHis%20parents%20were%20in%20the%20US%20in%20May%20for%20his%20convocation%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Texas.%20After%20the%20convocation%2C%20they%20asked%20him%20to%20return%20to%20India%2C%20but%20he%20said%20he%20wanted%20to%20work%20in%20the%20US%20for%20two%20more%20years.%20Fate%20has%20struck%20like%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20relative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOrampati's%20friend%20Shaik%2C%20too%2C%20was%20from%20Hyderabad%20and%20lived%20in%20Bentonville.%20Darshini%2C%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20was%20living%20in%20Frisco%2C%20Texas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarooq%20Shaik's%20father%20Masthan%20Vali%20said%20he%20went%20to%20the%20US%20three%20years%20back.%20%26quot%3BHe%20went%20to%20the%20US%20to%20complete%20his%20MS%20degree.%20He%20finished%20it%20recently.%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Vali%20is%20a%20retired%20private%20employee%20and%20the%20family%20lives%20in%20BHEL%20Hyderabad.%20%26quot%3BMy%20daughter%20also%20lives%20in%20US%20and%20is%20handling%20the%20situation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fm3otba0o_us-accident_625x300_04_September_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20a%20speeding%20truck%20rear-ended%20the%20SUV%20the%20victims%20were%20in.%20The%20car%20burst%20into%20flames%20and%20all%20the%20occupants%20burnt%20to%20death.%20The%20authorities%20are%20relying%20on%20DNA%20fingerprinting%20and%20teeth%20and%20bone%20remains%20to%20confirm%20the%20identities.%20%26quot%3BDNA%20fingerprinting%20will%20be%20done%20to%20identify%20the%20bodies%2C%20and%20the%20samples%20will%20be%20matched%20with%20the%20parents%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20local%20authority%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20long%20weekend%20in%20the%20US%20has%20delayed%20the%20identification%20process%2C%20prolonging%20the%20suffering%20of%20the%20victims'%20families.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725423840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fkaq1m594_indians-in-us-car-crash_650x400_04_September_24.jpg%22