0in%20Mumbai%20on%20Tuesday%20night%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShahana%20Kazmi%2C%20a%20mother%20of%20two%2C%20was%20returning%20home%20after%20a%20mehendi%20art%20class%20when%20a%20speeding%20Ford%20SUV%20rammed%20her%20in%20Malad%20West.%20The%20car%20crushed%20the%20young%20mother%20and%20dragged%20her%20to%20the%20road's%20divider%20before%20it%20stopped%2C%20locals%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20driver%20of%20the%20vehicle%20and%20the%20locals%20rushed%20the%20victim%20to%20a%20nearby%20hospital%20but%20she%20was%20declared%20dead.%20An%20angry%20mob%20thrashed%20the%20driver%20who%20was%20reportedly%20drunk.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVideos%20showed%20the%20driver%20crouching%20on%20the%20floor%20with%20a%20policeman%20standing%20next%20to%20him%20even%20as%20angry%20locals%20continue%20to%20hit%20him.%20The%20driver%20has%20been%20arrested%20and%20a%20case%20has%20been%20filed%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20months%20after%20the%20horrific%20Worli%20hit-and-run%20case%20where%20a%20woman%20was%20killed%20after%20she%20was%20dragged%20for%20a%20100%20metres%20when%20a%20speeding%20BMW%20hit%20her%20husband's%20two-wheeler.%20The%20car%20was%20driven%20by%20Mihir%20Shah%2C%20the%2024-year-son%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%20leader%20Rajesh%20Shah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20was%20arrested%20on%20July%209%2C%20two%20days%20after%20the%20accident.%20His%20driver%20Bidawat%2C%20who%20was%20also%20present%20in%20the%20car%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20accident%2C%20was%20arrested%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20alleged%20accident.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725422700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fqmkofom8_ford-accident_625x300_04_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmumbai-news%2F27-year-old-mother-of-2-killed-by-speeding-suv-in-mumbai-driver-arrested-6486194%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2027-year-old%20woman%20was%20killed%20after%20a%20speeding%20car%