g%20Tech%20executives%20look%20polished%20for%20work.%3Cp%3EJulia%20Blank%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJulia%20Blank%20is%20a%20personal%20stylist%20who%20helps%20Big%20Tech%20executives%20look%20their%20best.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20says%20these%20executives%20come%20to%20her%20because%20they%20don't%20want%20to%20look%20like%20techies%20or%20students.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBlank%20sends%20them%20home%20with%20a%20new%20wardrobe%2C%20new%20makeup%20skills%2C%20and%20a%20bottle%20of%20scent%20that%20suits%20them.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.julia-blank.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EJulia%20Blank%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20a%2045-year-old%20personal%20stylist%20and%20image%20consultant.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20my%20career%20working%20as%20a%20research%20analyst%20on%20Wall%20Street.%20During%20those%20years%2C%20I%20realized%20how%20sad%20the%20Wall%20Street%20scene%20had%20become%2C%20because%20the%20business%20formal%20attire%20was%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20a%20sudden%2C%20business%20casual%20took%20its%20place%2C%20and%20many%20men%20around%20me%20%E2%80%94%20working%20in%20the%20office%2C%20my%20buddies%2C%20my%20friends%20from%20college%20%E2%80%94%20were%20all%20looking%20at%20each%20other%2C%20thinking%2C%20what%20the%20hell%20is%20business%20casual%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20I%20was%20brought%20up%20in%20New%20York%2C%20I%20lived%20in%20stores%2C%20and%20fashion%20was%20my%20passion.%20I%20felt%20like%20Carrie%20Bradshaw%20from%20Sex%20and%20the%20City.%20I%20would%20just%20look%20at%20shoes%2C%20touch%20the%20fabrics%2C%20and%20admire%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20maternity%20leave%2C%20I%20realized%20styling%20was%20my%20true%20calling.%20I%20started%20slowly%20offering%20styling%20services%20to%20my%20sphere%20of%20influence%2C%20which%20included%20bankers%20and%20colleagues%20I%20used%20to%20work%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22aac0c61f-76b3-45b0-b8a6-2a361609b7db%5C%22%3EWhy%20Big%20Tech%20execs%20are%20on%20the%20hunt%20for%20personal%20stylists%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Julia%20Blank%20is%20a%20personal%20stylist%20in%20Singapore%20who%20helps%20Big%20Tech%20executives%20look%20polished%20for%20work.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66cc340343b5e59d16b5031a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221366%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBlank%20is%20based%20in%20Singapore%20and%20takes%20on%20clients%20from%20the%20technology%20sector.%20%3Cp%3EJulia%20Blank%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%2017%20years%2C%20I've%20been%20styling%20clients%20in%20Singapore.%20I've%20picked%20up%20a%20lot%20of%20clients%20from%20the%20technology%20sector%2C%20particularly%20companies%20like%20Google%2C%20Yahoo%2C%20Facebook%2C%20and%20LinkedIn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20feel%20that%20there%20is%20definitely%20a%20need%20to%20look%20like%20you're%20in%20a%20managerial%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20you're%20in%20a%20tech%20company%20where%20you%20can%20literally%20wear%20anything%20%E2%80%94%20where%20there's%20no%20dress%20code%E2%80%94%20it%20makes%20it%20that%20much%20more%20difficult%20to%20understand%20how%20to%20look%20presentable%20at%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParticularly%20managers%20come%20to%20me%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20look%20like%20a%20techie%20who%20programs%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20look%20like%20a%20lawyer%20wearing%20a%20business%20suit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20I%20don't%20understand.%20What%20do%20I%20wear%3F%26quot%3B%20they%20ask.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20reasons%20people%20want%20to%20change%20up%20their%20wardrobe.%20It%20could%20be%20you've%20got%20a%20job%20you%20didn't%20think%20you%20would%20get%2C%20and%20your%20wardrobe%20is%20still%20stuck%20in%20your%20past%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b48e98d4-cb0e-4d22-b4b6-8b3ad5403efe%5C%22%3EThe%20styling%20process%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Blank%20helps%20Tech%20execs%20dress%20for%20the%20top%20job.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d672ea289b805d1db37501%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221366%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBlank%20helps%20Tech%20execs%20dress%20for%20the%20top%20job.%3Cp%3EJulia%20Blank%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20time%20I%20meet%20a%20client%2C%20I%20spend%20about%20three%20and%20a%20half%20hours%20at%20a%20client's%20home%2C%20getting%20to%20know%20each%20other%2C%20taking%20measurements%2C%20and%20understanding%20the%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20consultation%2C%20I%20do%20a%20color%20analysis%2C%20and%20then%20the%20client%20opens%20up%20their%20wardrobe%20and%20shows%20me%20everything%20they've%20accumulated%20so%20far.%20This%20process%20is%20very%20important%20because%20I%20can%20gather%20a%20lot%20of%20insights%20that%20they%20will%20not%20tell%20you%20in%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%2C%20I%20put%20together%20a%20mood%20board%20of%20styles%20for%20a%20person.%20This%20is%20how%20I%20see%20them%20evolve%20with%20their%20style%20moving%20forward.%20Once%20they%20approve%20the%20mood%20board%2C%20we%20schedule%20a%20shopping%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20stylist%2C%20my%20prerogative%20is%20to%20give%20you%20clothes%20that%20make%20you%20feel%20comfortable%20and%20confident.%20It's%20not%20about%20spending%20lots%20of%20cash%20on%20things%20you%20don't%20need%3B%20my%20job%20is%20to%20look%20after%20your%20wallet%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20really%20love%20shopping%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.massimodutti.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMassimo%20Dutti%3C%2F