E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20had%20won%20five%20gold%2C%20eight%20silver%20and%20six%20bronze%20medals%20at%20the%20Tokyo%20Paralympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20javelin%20throwers%20continued%20to%20set%20the%20bar%20high%20with%20Ajeet%20Singh%20and%20world%20record%20holder%20Sundar%20Singh%20Gurjar%20clinching%20the%20silver%20and%20bronze%20with%20throws%20of%2065.62m%20and%2064.96m%20respectively%20in%20the%20F46%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EF46%20category%20is%20for%20field%20athletes%20with%20moderately%20affected%20movement%20in%20one%20or%20both%20arms%20or%20the%20absence%20of%20limbs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHigh%20jumpers%20Sharad%20Kumar%20and%20Tokyo%20Paralympics%20gold%20medallist%20Mariyappan%20Thangavelu%20gave%20it%20their%20all%20before%20settling%20for%20silver%20and%20bronze%20in%20the%20T63%20finals%2C%20with%20jumps%20of%201.88m%20and%201.85m%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ET63%20is%20for%20high%20jumpers%20with%20available%20movement%20moderately%20affected%20in%20one%20leg%20or%20the%20absence%20of%20limbs%20above%20the%20knee.%20Earlier%2C%20world%20champion%20sprinter%20Deepthi%20Jeevanji%20ensured%20another%20bronze%20for%20India%20in%20the%20women's%20400m%20(T20)%20event%20with%20the%2020-year-old%20clocking%2055.82sec%20to%20secure%20a%20podium%20finish%20in%20her%20debut%20Games%20appearance.%20She%20finished%20behind%20Yuliia%20Shuliar%20(55.16sec)%20of%20Ukraine%20and%20world%20record%20holder%20Aysel%20Onder%20(55.23sec)%20of%20Turkey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDaughter%20of%20farm%20labourers%20from%20Kalleda%20Village%20in%20Telangana's%20Warangal%20district%2C%20Jeevanji%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20intellectual%20impairment%20after%20being%20spotted%20at%20a%20school%20level%20athletics%20meet%20by%20one%20of%20her%20teachers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%2C%20she%20and%20her%20parents%20were%20subjected%20to%20taunts%20by%20natives%20of%20her%20village%20due%20to%20her%20disability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20same%20village%20has%20been%20celebrating%20her%20ever%20since%20she%20won%20a%20gold%20at%20last%20year's%20Asian%20Para%20Games%20before%20breaking%20the%20world%20record%20at%20the%20Para%20World%20Championships%20in%20May%20this%20year%20to%20fetch%20another%20gold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20youngster%20was%20also%20assisted%20by%20national%20badminton%20coach%20Pullela%20Gopichand%20after%20she%20began%20training%20with%20her%20formative%20coach%20Nagpuri%20Ramesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20T20%20category%20is%20meant%20for%20athletes%20who%20have%20intellectual%20impairment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELekhara's%20campaign%20ends%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20ace%20Indian%20shooter%20Avani%20Lekhara%20missed%20out%20on%20a%20second%20medal%20at%20the%20Games%20as%20she%20finished%20fifth%20in%20the%20final%20of%20the%20women's%2050m%20rifle%203%20positions%20SH1%20competition%20in%20Chateauroux.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2022-year-old%2C%20paralysed%20waist-down%20at%2011%20years%20of%20age%20owing%20to%20a%20car%20accident%2C%20shot%20a%20total%20of%20420.6%20across%20the%20three%20stages%20of%20kneeling%2C%20prone%20and%20standing%20in%20a%20world-class%20eight-woman%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20she%20has%20lots%20to%20celebrate%20after%20becoming%20first%20Indian%20woman%20to%20win%20consecutive%20gold%20medals%20at%20Paralympics%20following%20a%20top%20finish%20in%20the%2010m%20air%20rifle%20competition%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGermany's%20Natascha%20Hiltrop%20won%20the%20gold%20with%20a%20total%20of%20456.5%2C%20Slovakian%20Veronika%20Vadovicova%20claimed%20silver%20with%20456.1%2C%20and%20China's%20Zhang%20shot%20446.0%20to%20bag%20the%20bronze.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SH1%20class%20is%20designated%20for%20athletes%20with%20lower-limb%20impairment%20for%20competition%20in%20rifle%20shooting%20events.%20Here%20shooters%20are%20able%20hold%20their%20gun%20without%20difficulty%20and%20shoot%20from%20a%20standing%20or%20sitting%20position%20(in%20a%20wheelchair%20or%20chair).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJadhav%20ends%205th%20in%20shot%20put%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhagyashri%20Jadhav%20finished%20fifth%20in%20the%20women's%20shot%20put%20(F34).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJadhav%2C%20making%20her%20second%20appearance%20at%20the%20Paralympics%2C%20produced%20a%20throw%20of%207.28m%20but%20it%20was%20not%20enough%20for%20a%20podium%20finish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina's%20Lijuan%20Zou%20won%20the%20gold%20with%20a%20season's%20best%20of%209.14m%20while%20Poland's%20Lucyna%20Kornobys%20secured%20the%20silver%20with%20an%20effort%20of%208.33m.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2039-year-old%20Indian%2C%20who%20hails%20from%20Nanded%20district%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20is%20an%20inspiring%20story%20of%20resilience.%20She%20slipped%20into%20depression%20after%20losing%20the%20use%20of%20her%20legs%20due%20to%20an%20accident%20in%202006.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20she%20fought%20back%20to%20reclaim%20her%20life%20as%20a%20para-athlete%20with%20help%20from%20friends%20and%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArcher%20Pooja's%20campaign%20ends%20in%20quarters%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorld%20Para%20Championship%20silver%20medallist%20Pooja%20Jatyan%20beat%20Yagmur%20Sengul%20of%20Turkey%20in%20straight%20sets%20to%20storm%20into%20the%20quarterfinals%20of%20recurve%20women's%20open%20archery%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%2027-year-old%20could%20not%20sustain%20the%20momentum%20and%20lost%20to%20Tokyo%20Paralympics%20bronze-medallist%20Wu%20Chunyan%20of%20China%20in%20the%20last-eight%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20particularly%20painful%20loss%20to%20Chunyan%20given%20that%20Pooja%20led%204-0%20at%20one%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20winner%20of%20four%20Paralympics%20medals%2C%20including%20a%20team%20gold%20in%202016%20Rio%20Games%2C%20the%2034-year-old%20Chinese%20archer%20was%20nowhere%20in%20the%20picture%20after%20a%20disastrous%20opening%2