re%20playing%20all%20three%20formats.%20If%20Shaheen%20has%20played%20consistently%20for%20a%20year%2C%20you%20can't%20just%20throw%20them%20in%20every%20game.%20And%20you%20have%20to%20build%20up%20your%20stocks%20as%20well.%20So%20we've%20got%20a%20lot%20to%20look%20at%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Day%204%2C%20the%20Pakistan%20Test%20head%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jason%20Gillespie%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F203-jason-gillespie-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJason%20Gillespie%3C%2Fa%3E%20addressed%20the%20omission%20of%20Shaheen%20and%20Naseem%20from%20the%20playing%20XI%20and%20highlighted%20that%20the%20team%20is%20not%20looking%20to%20rely%20on%20individuals.%20The%20iconic%20Australian%20pacer%20stated%20that%20he%20wants%20to%20see%20Shaheen%20peak%20and%20start%20firing%20at%20the%20top%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20few%20things%20that%20we%20are%20hoping%20Shaheen%20can%20work%20on.%20He%20had%20a%20pretty%20eventful%20time%20in%20his%20personal%20life%20as%20well.%20We%20want%20Shaheen%20Afridi%20to%20be%20at%20his%20very%20best%20for%20as%20much%20cricket%20as%20possible.%20He%20is%20an%20all-format%20player%2C%20and%20we%20have%20a%20pretty%20heavy%20schedule%2C%20and%20we%20want%20him%20to%20be%20fit%20and%20firing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaseem%20and%20Shaheen%20had%20a%20mediocre%20T20%20World%20Cup%2C%20which%20saw%20Pakistan%20crash%20out%20in%20the%20group%20stage.%20Both%20pacers%20scythed%20five%20wickets%20each%20despite%20playing%20on%20a%20surface%20that%20assisted%20the%20pacers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20bowlers%20could%20not%20do%20much%20in%20the%20first%20Test.%20Pakistan%20lost%20the%20second%20Test%20as%20well%20suffering%20a%20series%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725417300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fpv5m4fl_shan-masood_625x300_03_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fcant-just-throw-them-in-every-game-shan-masoods-blunt-take-on-dropping-shaheen-afridi-naseem-shah-6483845%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pakistan%20captain%20Shan%20Masood%20backed%20the%20decision%20to%20exclude%20Shaheen%20and%20Naseem%20from%20the%20second%20Test%20against%20Bangladesh%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fcant-just-throw-them-in-every-game-shan-masoods-blunt-take-on-dropping-shaheen-afridi-naseem-shah-6483845%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Called%20'Monkey%2C%20Mental'%20By%20Villagers%2C%20Deepthi%20Achieves%20Paralympics%20Glory%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Paris%20Paralympics%202024%20has%20shown%20the%20world%20that%20anything%20is%20achievable%20if%20one%20has%20the%20will.%20The%20athletes%2C%20despite%20challenges%2C%20have%20risen%20to%20glory.%20India's%20Deepthi%20Jeevanji%20is%20among%20those%20inspirational%20athletes%20whose%20journey%20was%20full%20of%20challenges%2C%20but%20they%20never%20gave%20up.%C2%A0Deepthi%20Jeevanji%20bagged%20the%2016th%20medal%20for%20India%20as%20she%20won%20the%20bronze%20on%20Tuesday%20in%20the%20women's%20400m%20T20%20final%20at%20the%20ongoing%20Paris%20Paralympics%202024.%20The%20para-athlete%20finished%20the%20race%20in%2055.82%20seconds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepthi%20Jeevanji%20had%20earlier%20won%20India's%20first%20gold%20medal%20at%20the%20World%20Athletics%20Para%20Championship%20in%20Kobe%2C%20Japan.%C2%A0She%20hails%20from%20the%20village%20of%20Kalleda%20in%20the%20Warangal%20district%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20parents%2C%20Jeevanji%20Yadhagiri%20and%20Jeevanji%20Dhanalaxmi%2C%20had%20then%20recalled%20how%20their%20daughter%20had%20to%20face%20taunts%20while%20growing%20up.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20in%20The%20Indian%20Express%2C%20Deepthi%20was%20born%20with%20intellectual%20disability%2C%20a%20cognitive%20disease%20hampering%20communication%20as%20well%20as%20adaptive%20skills.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShe%20was%20born%20during%20the%20solar%20eclipse%20and%20her%20head%20was%20very%20small%20at%20birth%20along%20with%20the%20lips%20and%20nose%20being%20a%20bit%20unusual.%20Every%20villager%20who%20saw%20her%20and%20some%20of%20our%20relatives%20would%20call%20Deepthi%20pichi%20(mental)%20and%20kothi%20(monkey)%20and%20tell%20us%20to%20send%20her%20to%20an%20orphanage.%20Today%2C%20seeing%20her%20become%20the%20world%20champion%20in%20a%20far-off%20country%20proves%20that%20she%20is%20indeed%20a%20special%20girl%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jeevanji%20Dhanalaxmi%2C%20Deepthi's%20mother%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fsports%2Fsport-others%2Fdeepthi-jeevanji-india-gold-medal-400m-world-record-para-championship-paris-paralympics-9341210%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20my%20husband's%20father%20died%2C%20we%20had%20to%20sell%20the%20farm%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%20My%20husband%20would%20earn%20Rs%20100%20or%20Rs%20150%20a%20day%20so%20there%20were%20days%20when%20I%20had%20to%20work%20to%20support%20our%20family%2C%20including%20Deepthi's%20younger%20sister%20Amulya.%20Deepthi%20was%20always%20a%20calm%20child%20and%20spoke%20very%20little.%20But%20when%20the%20village%20kids%20would%20tease%20her%2C%20she%20would%20come%20home%20and%20cry.%20So%20I%20would%20make%20her%20sweet%20rice%20or%2C%20on%20some%20days%2C%20chicken%20and%20that's%20what%20made%20her%20happy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20her%20daughter's%20big%20feat%2C%20Jeevanji's%20father%20Yadhagiri%20was%20emotional.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20though%20it's%20a%20big%20day%20for%20all%20of%20us%2C%20I%20could%20not%20afford%20to%20miss%20work.%20That's%20my%20bread%20and%20butter%20and%20the%20whole%20day%20I%20was%20thinking%20about%20Deepthi%20winning%20a%20medal%20in%20Paris%20and%20would%20tell%20the%20driver%20Elfer%20about%20calling%20other%20friends%20and%20their%20families%20to%20celebrate%20Deepthi's%20medal.%20She%20has%20always%20given%20us%20joy%20and%20this%20medal%20will%20also%20mean%20a%20lot%20to%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725417120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Ff9g6bph_deepthi-jeevanji-_625x300_04_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fparalympic-games-2024%2Fcalled-monkey-mental-by-fellow-villagers-deepthi-jeevanji-fights-taboo-to-achieve-paralympics-glory-6484617%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Deepthi%20Jeevanji%20bagged%20the%2016th%20medal%20for%20India%20as%20she%20won%20the%20bronze%20on%20Tuesday%20in%20the%20women's%20400m%20T20%20final%20at%20the%20ongoing%20Paris%20Paralympics%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fparalympic-games-2024%2Fcalled-monkey-mental-by-fellow-villagers-deepthi-jeevanji-fights-taboo-to-achieve-paralympics-glory-6484617%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20elections%3A%20Campaign%20launched%20to%20increase%20participation%20of%20Indian-Americans%20in%20polls%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725417005000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113047616%2Cimgsize-830480.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-elections-campaign-launched-to-increase-participation-of-indian-americans-in-polls%2Farticleshow%2F113047598.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F113047598.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20Foundation%20for%20India%20and%20Indian%20Diaspora%20Studies%20(FIIDS)%20has%20launched%20the%20'Indo%20American%20Votes%20Matter'%20campaign%20to%20increase%20the%20policy%20impa