ow%2F113046622.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Robert%20F%20Kennedy%20will%20still%20face%20Trump%20despite%20endorsing%20him%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725415746000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113047316%2Cimgsize-21652.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwhy-robert-f-kennedy-will-still-face-trump-despite-endorsing-him%2Farticleshow%2F113047007.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Robert%20F%20Kennedy%20Jr's%20effort%20to%20remove%20his%20name%20from%20Michigan's%20presidential%20ballot%20has%20been%20denied%20by%20a%20judge.%20Despite%20suspending%20his%20campaign%20and%20endorsing%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20Kennedy%20must%20stay%20on%20the%20ballot%20due%20to%20state%20laws.%20Similar%20legal%20challenges%20are%20ongoing%20in%20other%20states%2C%20reflecting%20the%20intricate%20nature%20of%20election%20regulations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20WORLD%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwhy-robert-f-kennedy-will-still-face-trump-despite-endorsing-him%2Farticleshow%2F113047007.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Australian%20Air%20Traffic%20Controller%20Found%20Asleep%20Under%20A%20Blanket%20Mid-Shift%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAustralia's%20air%20safety%20investigators%20have%20recommended%20reforms%20after%20a%20Brisbane%20air%20traffic%20controller%20was%20found%20asleep%20at%20his%20desk%20while%20covering%20an%20early-morning%20shift.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20by%20the%20Australian%20Transport%20Safety%20Bureau%20(ATSB)%2C%20the%20staffer%20was%20managing%20the%20Cairns%20Terminal%20Control%20Unit%20(TCU)%20from%20Airservices%20Australia's%20Brisbane%20office%20when%20he%20was%20discovered%20asleep%20by%20the%20oncoming%20air%20traffic%20controller%20who%20was%20working%20the%20day%20shift.%20The%20incident%20took%20place%20in%20December%202022.%20In%20its%20report%2C%20released%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20ATSB%20blamed%20multiple%20consecutive%20night%20shifts%20and%20an%20ineffective%20fatigue%20risk%20management%20system%20for%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2C%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.atsb.gov.au%2Fmedia%2Fnews-items%2F2024%2Ffatigue-management-improvements-underway-after-brisbane-centre-controller-found-asleep-end-their-night-shift%5C%22%3EATSB%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20staffer%20was%20found%20lying%20across%20two%20chairs%20and%20under%20a%20blanket%20at%20the%20end%20of%20a%20night%20shift.%20The%20employee%20had%20worked%20their%20seventh%20night%20shift%20in%20nine%20days%20as%20an%20approach%20controller%20for%20Cairns%20airport%20from%20the%20Brisbane%20control%20centre%2C%20with%20the%20shift%20starting%20at%2010%20pm%20and%20running%20until%206%20am.%20The%20staffer%20had%20completed%2010%20night%20shifts%20in%2012%20days.%20The%20report%20stated%20that%20there%20were%20no%20planes%20in%20the%20area%20at%20the%20time%20and%20ATSB%20was%20unable%20to%20determine%20when%20the%20employee%20went%20to%20sleep.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20the%20investigation%20report%20details%20on%20X%2C%20ATSB%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20Brisbane%20Centre%20air%20traffic%20controller%20who%20was%20found%20asleep%20at%20their%20workstation%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20their%20shift%20had%20worked%20multiple%20consecutive%20night%20shifts%20resulting%20in%20sleep%20debt%2C%20an%20ATSB%20investigation%20report%20details.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EA%20Brisbane%20Centre%20air%20traffic%20controller%20who%20was%20found%20asleep%20at%20their%20workstation%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20their%20shift%20had%20worked%20multiple%20consecutive%20night%20shifts%20resulting%20in%20sleep%20debt%2C%20an%20ATSB%20investigation%20report%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ATSB%20(%40atsbgovau)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fatsbgovau%2Fstatus%2F1830791268907278639%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%203%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20press%20note%2C%20ATSB%20Chief%20Commissioner%20Angus%20Mitchell%20said%20there%20were%20several%20factors%20contributing%20to%20the%20staffer%20falling%20asleep%20on%20the%20job%20but%20stressed%20the%20staffer's%20fatigue%20was%20a%20key%20component%20as%20they%20had%20worked%2010-night%20shifts%20in%20the%20previous%2012%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20controller%20had%20also%20been%20working%20multiple%20night%20shifts%20with%20reduced%20extended%20rest%20periods%2C%20which%20likely%20reduced%20their%20ability%20to%20obtain%20restorative%20sleep%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mitchell%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlongside%20the%20staffer's%20fatigue%2C%20the%20ATSB%20noted%20the%20time%20of%20day%20the%20controller%20was%20working%2C%20the%20low%20workload%20in%20a%20night%20shift%2C%20the%20employee%20not%20undertaking%20mental%20alertness%20activities%20and%20lying%20down%20on%20two%20chairs%20under%20a%20blanket.%20It%20also%20said%20that%20the%20controller%20may%20have%20experienced%20%26quot%3Bsleep%20inertia%26quot%3B%20after%20waking%20up%2C%20impacting%20their%20ability%20to%20communicate%20and%20make%20decisions%20during%20an%20instance%20where%20traffic%20infringes%20on%20their%20airspace.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20no%20negative%20consequences%20from%20this%20occurrence%2C%20but%20it%20does%20highlight%20areas%20for%20improvement%20in%20work%20scheduling%20and%20fatigue%20risk%20management%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Mitchell.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjunior-doctors-death-in-indonesia-exposes-open-secret-of-bullying-in-medical-schools-6479344%5C%22%3EJunior%20Doctor's%20Death%20In%20Indonesia%20Exposes%20%26quot%3BOpen%20Secret%26quot%3B%20Of%20Bullying%20In%20Medical%20Schools%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ATSB%20report%20further%20criticised%20an%20%26quot%3Bover-reliance%26quot%3B%20on%20short-term%20changes%20to%20manage%20the%20airport%20roster%20%26quot%3Blikely%20due%20to%20an%20underlying%20lack%20of%20resources%20within%20Airservices%20Australia%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BAs%20a%20result%2C%20cumulative%20fatigue%20was%20not%20being%20effectively%20managed%20strategically%2C%20and%20an%20over-reliance%20on%20tactical%20principles%20did%20not%20identify%20or%20manage%20fatigue%20risks%20arising%20from%20the%20work%20schedule%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20Airservices%20upped%20its%20overall%20number%20of%20air%20traffic%20controllers%2C%20the%20Guardian%20reported.%20The%20Civil%20Aviation%20Safety%20Authority%20also%20announced%20changes%20to%20its%20fatigue%20risk%20management%20system%20requirement%20and%20is%20working%20alongside%20Airservices%20to%20bolster%20its%20approach%20to%20staffer%20fatigue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mitchell%20called%20on%20other%20sectors%20of%20the%20transport%20industry%20to%20put%20the%20spotlight%20on%20fatigue%20as%20a%20danger%20in%20the%20workplace.%20%26quot%3BFatigue%20remains%20one%20of%20the%20most%20relevant%20ongoing%20concerns%20for%20safe%20transport%2C%20despite%20increased%20awareness%20across%20the%20transport%20sector%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725415440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F30vmmuoo_airport-generic_625x300_04_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Faustralian-air-traffic-controller-found-sleeping-on-duty-after-10-night-shifts-in-12-days-6485743%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Australia's%20air%20safety%20investigators%20have%20recommended%20reforms%20after%20a%20Brisbane%20