n%20and%20technology%20hardware%20used%20in%20artificial%20intelligence%20applications%20and%20other%20projects%2C%20the%20department%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20in%20August%202022%20approved%20a%20%2439%20billion%20subsidy%20program%20for%20U.S.%20semiconductor%20manufacturing%20and%20related%20components%20along%20with%20%2475%20billion%20in%20government%20lending%20authority%20and%20a%2025%25%20investment%20tax%20credit%20worth%20an%20estimated%20%2424%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20projects%20build%20on%20HP's%20expertise%20in%20microfluidics%20and%20microelectromechanical%20systems%20with%20funding%20set%20to%20support%20manufacturing%20of%20silicon%20devices%20critical%20in%20life%20sciences%20lab%20equipment%20used%20in%20drug%20discovery%2C%20singlecell%20research%2C%20and%20cell%20line%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommerce%20Secretary%20Gina%20Raimondo%20said%20the%20proposed%20%2450%20million%20funding%20for%20the%20Corvallis%2C%20Oregon%2C%20HP%20campus%20%26quot%3Bshows%20how%20we%20are%20investing%20in%20every%20part%20of%20the%20semiconductor%20supply%20chain%20and%20how%20important%20semiconductor%20technology%20is%20to%20innovation%20in%20drug%20discovery%20and%20critical%20life%20science%20equipment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20department%20said%20the%20technology%20will%20boost%20partner%20institutions%20including%20Harvard%20Medical%20School%2C%20the%20U.S.%20Centers%20for%20Disease%20Control%20and%20Prevention%2C%20and%20Merck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHP%20CEO%20Enrique%20Lores%20said%20the%20funding%20%26quot%3Bprovides%20HP%20with%20an%20opportunity%20to%20modernize%20and%20expand%20our%20facility%20to%20further%20invest%20in%20our%20microfluidics%20technology.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20department%20has%20announced%20term%20sheets%20with%2017%20companies%20offering%20more%20than%20%2432%20billion%20in%20grants%20and%20up%20to%20%2429%20billion%20in%20loans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20made%20other%20majo