%20Oldest%20Crocodile%20Henry%20Who%20Has%206%20Wives%20And%2010%2C000%20Babies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20enormous%2016ft%20beast%20weighing%20700%20kg%20and%20fathering%20thousands%20of%20hatchlings%20is%20now%20recognised%20as%20the%20world's%20oldest%20crocodile.%20Meet%20Henry%2C%20the%20man-eating%20Nile%20crocodile%2C%20who%20at%20123%20years%20old%20has%20sired%20over%2010%2C000%20babies%20with%20his%20six%20%E2%80%98wives%2C'%20according%20to%20the%20zoo%20where%20he%20lives.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHenry's%20journey%20began%20in%20the%20Okavango%20Delta%2C%20Botswana%2C%20a%20UNESCO%20World%20Heritage%20Site%2C%20where%20he%20was%20born%20on%20December%2016%2C%201900%2C%20as%20per%20the%20Sun.%20Renowned%20for%20his%20terrifying%20fang-like%20teeth%20and%20massive%20frame%2C%20Henry%20is%20now%20believed%20to%20be%20the%20largest%20living%20crocodile%2C%20with%20a%20length%20that%20almost%20matches%20a%20minibus.%20However%2C%20his%20past%20is%20far%20from%20ordinary.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20the%20early%201900s%2C%20Henry%20developed%20a%20notorious%20reputation%20among%20the%20local%20tribes%20in%20Botswana%2C%20where%20he%20allegedly%20preyed%20on%20human%20children.%20The%20tribes%2C%20desperate%20to%20end%20his%20bloodthirsty%20reign%2C%20sought%20the%20help%20of%20a%20famed%20hunter%2C%20Sir%20Henry%20Neumann%2C%20after%20whom%20the%20crocodile%20was%20named.%20Rather%20than%20killing%20the%20beast%2C%20Mr%20Neumann%20captured%20Henry%2C%20sentencing%20him%20to%20a%20lifetime%20of%20captivity.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnFor%20the%20past%20three%20decades%2C%20Henry%20has%20lived%20at%20the%20Crocworld%20Conservation%20Centre%20in%20Scottburgh%2C%20South%20Africa.%20There%2C%20he%20continues%20to%20awe%20visitors%20with%20his%20size%20and%20age%2C%20making%20him%20one%20of%20the%20oldest%20crocodiles%20in%20captivity.%20His%20dark%2C%20man-eating%20past%20is%20a%20stark%20contrast%20to%20his%20current%20life%20as%20a%20zoo%20attract