-41bf-a7c2-153fdeee98e9%5C%22%3EFacing%20challenges%20during%20the%20process%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20materials%2C%20right%20down%20to%20the%20type%20of%20tiles%2C%20that%20were%20used%20in%20the%20home%20were%20chosen%20by%20his%20wife%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20three-bedroom%20home%20has%20two%20floors.%20The%20master%20bedroom%2C%20a%20family%20room%2C%20and%20a%20bathroom%20are%20on%20the%20first%20floor.%20The%20kitchen%2C%20living%20area%2C%20and%20the%20kids'%20bedrooms%20are%20upstairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20main%20living%20space%20that%20I%20spend%20the%20most%20time%20in%20is%20kind%20of%20the%20kitchen%20and%20living%20room%20area%2C%20so%20I%20wanted%20that%20to%20be%20gorgeous%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20rice%20fields%20around%2C%20and%20mountains%20in%20the%20back%2C%20but%20when%20you're%20at%20the%20first%20floor%2C%20you%20can't%20really%20see%20very%20far.%20So%20we%20moved%20everything%20up%20to%20the%20second%20floor.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222155%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20open-plan%20kitchen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bee5b2b4912df3ae1c388b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221616%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20open-plan%20kitchen.%3Cp%3EJordan%2C%20Inside%20Outsider%20in%20Japan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20building%20company%20they%20worked%20with%20mostly%20did%20carpentry%20work%2C%20so%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecertain%20jobs%20%E2%80%94%20like%20wiring%20and%20plumbing%20%E2%80%94%20had%20to%20be%20outsourced%20to%20different%20contractors.%20This%20sometimes%20led%20to%20miscommunication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20would%20come%20in%2C%20and%20we'd%20have%20this%20vision%20for%20our%20house%20that%20I'd%20assume%20everyone%20would%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20Jordan%20said.%20%26quot%3BOur%20carpenter%20gets%20it.%20But%20what%20happens%20is%20when%20you%20hire%20an%20outside%20company%2C%20they%20come%20in%2C%20they%20look%20at%20it%2C%20and%20they%20do%20what%20they%20normally%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20family%20room%20downstairs.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bc5d2f5da406397bf5b7ab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221620%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20family%20room%20downstairs.%3Cp%3EJordan%2C%20Inside%20Outsider%20in%20Japan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20things%20were%20happening%20in%20a%20way%20that%20wasn't%20what%20we%20thought%20we%20agreed%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20everything%20was%20sorted%20out%20in%20the%20end%2C%20there%20were%20moments%20when%20he%20worried%20that%20things%20wouldn't%20work%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20it%20helped%20that%20his%20wife%20and%20her%20family%20were%20involved%20in%20communicating%20ideas%20to%20the%20builders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can%20speak%20Japanese%2C%20but%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20nuance.%20It%20would've%20been%20really%20difficult%20if%20it%20was%20down%20to%20me%20explaining%20stuff%20in%20Japanese%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fc6b65df-b6a4-47df-b9d8-0cfab76f20c9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAppreciating%20Japanese%20culture%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJordan%20says%20he%20succeeded%20in%20building%20a%20space%20that's%20perfect%20for%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222079%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20house%20as%20viewed%20from%20the%20side.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bee5455da406397bf6787b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221559%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20house%20has%20two%20floors%20and%20overlooks%20some%20rice%20fields.%3Cp%3EJordan%2C%20Inside%20Outsider%20in%20Japan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20differences%20is%20we%20don't%20feel%20like%20going%20out%20as%20much%20now%20because%20it's%20just%20comfortable%20to%20be%20at%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20Jordan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20also%20close%20to%20the%20local%20community%2C%20and%20it's%20one%20of%20the%20things%20he%20really%20likes%20about%20Japanese%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20also%20kind%20of%20an%20Asian%20thing.%20It%20sounds%20negative%2C%20but%20the%20minimization%20of%20the%20self%20for%20the%20good%20of%20the%20community%20%E2%80%94%20you%20learn%20how%20to%20pull%20yourself%20in%20a%20little%20bit%20for%20the%20good%20of%20everyone%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20Jordan%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20think%20about%20how%20it%20makes%20everyone%20around%20you%20feel.%20That%20kind%20of%20thing%20is%20very%20practical%20and%20it%20makes%20for%20a%20community%20that%20feels%20good%20to%20be%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222152%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20sitting%20on%20his%20patio.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bee66d5da406397bf6788d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221614%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJordan%20says%20the%20best%20part%20of%20being%20in%20the%20rural%20countryside%20of%20Japan%20is%20the%20laidback%20lifestyle.%3Cp%3EJordan%2C%20Inside%20Outsider%20in%20Japan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20likes%20the%20attitude%20the%20Japanese%20have%20toward%20working%20hard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20other%20thing%20is%2C%20in%20Japan%2C%20in%20general%2C%20if%20people%20are%20going%20to%20do%20something%2C%20they%20want%20to%20do%20it%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20love%20the%20feeling%20that%20people%20take%20pride%20in%20what%20they%20do%20and%20that%20people%20respect%20others%20for%20hard%20work%2C%20whatever%20the%20work%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224d4cfcf1-0f89-44ec-bddf-7fb98666bd64%5C%22%3EA%20laid-back%20life%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJordan%20isn't%20alone%20in%20being%20drawn%20to%20Japan.%20According%20to%20the%20country's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moj.go.jp%2Fisa%2Fcontent%2F001415139.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMinistry%20of%20Justice%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%202%2C604%20Americans%20moved%20to%20the%20country%20in%202023%2C%20bringing%20the%20total%20number%20of%20American%20expats%20in%20Japan%20to%2063%2C408.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFour%20Americans%20that%20BI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famericans-moving-to-japan-safety-affordability-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20spoke%20with%3C%2Fa%3E%20cite%20the%20country's%20safety%20standards%20and%20relative%20affordability%20as%20reasons%20for%20making%20the%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20Jordan%2C%20many%20of%20these%20expats%20are%20also%20opting%20to%20live%20in%20the%20countryside%20where%20they%20can%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-to-japanese-countryside-raising-children-safety-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eenjoy%20a%20slower-paced%20life%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20being%20surrounded%20by%20the%20stunning%20natural%20landscapes%20that%20Japan%20is%20known%20for.%20Some%20of%20them%20even%20choose%20to%20buy%20and%20renovate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-abandoned-houses-renovations-dream-homes-akiya-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20of%20the%20country's%208%20million%20abandoned%20homes%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20Jordan%2C%20he%20loves%20life%20in%20Japan%20so%20much%20that%20he's%20started%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2F%40Jordan-inJapan%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%20channel%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20document%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20really%20motivated%20me%20was%20that%20after%20living%20in%20Japan%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20I%20noticed%20that%20I%20stopped%20appreciating%20the%20little%20things.%20I%20lost%20that%20fresh%