.insider.com%2F66c8d27a1aa2ac29ee33ca7a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20new%20camera%20oval%20sticks%20out%20quite%20a%20bit%2C%20but%20the%20Pixel%209%20doesn't%20rock%20when%20placed%20on%20a%20flat%20surface.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20differentiating%20its%20looks%2C%20the%20Pixel%209's%20camera%20oval%20keeps%20the%20phone%20from%20rocking%20to%20one%20side%20on%20a%20flat%20surface%20when%20you're%20swiping%20and%20tapping%20on%20the%20screen%2C%20an%20issue%20with%20Apple's%20and%20Samsung's%20flagships%20due%20to%20their%20off-center%20cameras.%20It's%20not%20a%20reason%20on%20its%20own%20to%20buy%20the%20Pixel%209%20over%20other%20phones%20with%20offset%20cameras%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20nice%20benefit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Performance%5C%22%3EPerformance%3A%20Don't%20be%20disappointed%20by%20the%20lower%20benchmark%20results%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fgoogle-pixel-9-pro-xl-fold-release-date-price-features-specs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPixel%209%20series%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20the%20base%20and%20Pro%20models%2C%20run%20on%20Google's%20latest%20Tensor%20G4%20processor.%20The%20base%20Pixel%209%20behaves%20like%20a%20premium%20phone%20by%20opening%20and%20running%20apps%20quickly%20and%20smoothly.%20The%20same%20goes%20for%20games%2C%20which%20look%20sharp%20and%20detailed.%20And%20for%20most%20people%2C%20that's%20all%20that%20matters.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20in%20line%20with%20any%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-google-pixel-phone%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20Google%20Pixel%20phones%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Pixel%209%20doesn't%20benchmark%20like%20a%20top-tier%20device.%20Benchmark%20results%20show%20that%20the%20Pixel%209%20running%20the%20Tensor%20G4%20doesn't%20closely%20compete%20on%20performance%20with%20Qualcomm's%20Snapdragon%208%20Gen%203%20processor%20running%20Samsung's%20Galaxy%20S24%20series.%20In%20fact%2C%20it's%20not%20much%20of%20an%20upgrade%20over%20the%20previous-generation%20Tensor%20G3%20that%20ran%20the%20Pixel%208%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20only%20concern%20is%20whether%20the%20Pixel%209%20will%20stay%20quick%20and%20smooth%20for%20as%20many%20years%20as%20one%20would%20expect%20for%20a%20premium%20phone%20when%20the%20Android%20operating%20system%20and%20apps%20become%20more%20complex%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Pixel%209%20held%20in%20a%20hand%20against%20a%20desk%20and%20keyboard%20background%20while%20playing%20a%20car%20racing%20game.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c8d95b43b5e59d16b4cb12%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Pixel%209%20runs%20apps%20and%20games%20like%20any%20other%20premium%20phone%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20as%20powerful%20as%20other%20phones%20in%20its%20class.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3EUsing%20the%20Pixel%206%20with%20the%20original%20Google%20Tensor%20processor%20from%202021%20running%20the%20latest%20Android%2014%20as%20a%20point%20of%20reference%2C%20the%20Pixel%209%20should%20still%20run%20flawlessly%20after%20three%20years%20and%20two%20Android%20upgrades.%20Games%20don't%20look%20as%20crisp%20as%20on%20the%20Pixel%209%2C%20but%20the%20Pixel%206%20still%20runs%20great.%3Cp%3EIt%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20how%20many%20more%20years%20Google's%20Tensor%20processor%20can%20remain%20snappy%2C%20but%20if%20you%20upgrade%20your%20phones%20every%20two%20or%20three%20years%2C%20I'm%20confident%20in%20saying%20you%20shouldn't%20have%20anything%20to%20worry%20about%20with%20the%20Pixel%209's%20more%20powerful%20processor%20staying%20in%20working%20order%20for%20the%20long%20run.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20base%20Pixel%209%20has%20less%20RAM%20(12GB)%20than%20the%20Pixel%209%20Pro%20models%20(16GB)%2C%20but%20the%20difference%20is%20negligible%20in%20everyday%20use%20or%20with%20power-hungry%20applications%20like%20games.%20The%20Pixel%209%20also%20has%204GB%20more%20RAM%20than%20the%20previous%20Pixel%208%20to%20better%20accommodate%20Google's%20emergent%20AI%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Display%5C%22%3EDisplay%3A%20Brighter%20than%20ever%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Pixel%209's%206.3-inch%20display%20is%20on%20the%20larger%20side%20of%20the%20average%20for%20an%20entry-level%20flagship%20phone%20display%20(6.1%20inches)%2C%20but%20it's%20the%20smaller%20model%20in%20the%20series%20and%20feels%20perfectly%20manageable.%20The%20display%20can%20also%20run%20up%20to%20120Hz%2C%20but%20it's%20oddly%20set%20to%2060Hz%20by%20default.%20Make%20sure%20to%20enable%20%26quot%3BSmooth%20Scrolling%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20settings%20if%20you're%20after%20fluid%20on-screen%20animations%20that%20are%20standard%20on%20many%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-android-phone%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20Android%20phones%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20budget%20or%20premium.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20gave%20the%20base%20Pixel%209%20its%20super-bright%20Actua%20display%2C%20previously%20reserved%20for%20the%20Pro%20models%20in%20the%20Pixel%208%20series%2C%20that%20can%20reach%20up%20to%202700%20nit%20brightness.%20Viewing%20screen%20content%20under%20bright%20sunlight%20was%20never%20an%20issue%20in%20previous%20Pixels%2C%20but%20colors%20pop%20more%2C%20and%20content%20looks%20better%20overall%20on%20the%20Pixel%209's%20Actua%20display.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Pixel%209%20held%20in%20hand%20against%20a%20desk%20background%20with%20a%20mouse%20and%20keyboard%20visible%20showing%20the%20home%20screen%20with%20app%20icons.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c8dc7ec72ebc54a40e7600%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Pixel%209%20has%20a%206.3-inch%20display%2C%20which%20is%20slightly%20larger%20than%20previous%20generations.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20bit%20late%20to%20the%20party%2C%20but%20Google%20finally%20adopted%20a%20modern%20ultrasonic%20fingerprint%20sensor%20system%20for%20the%20Pixel%209%20after%20using%20outdated%20optical%20sensors.%20It's%20extremely%20quick%20and%20accurate%2C%20and%20it's%20better%20than%20the%20ultrasonic%20fingerprint%20sensors%20on%20Samsung's%20Galaxy%20S24%20series%2C%20which%20consistently%20give%20me%20trouble%20unlocking%20the%20phone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Pixel%209%20uses%20more%20basic%20face%20recognition%20than%20Apple's%20Face%20ID%2C%20but%20it%20works%20surprisingly%20similarly.%20I've%20found%20it's%20fast%20to%20unlock%20the%20phone%20and%20more%20reliable%20than%20Samsung's%20face%20recognition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Battery%20life%5C%22%3EBattery%20life%3A%20Excellent%2C%20but%20nothing%20extraordinary%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20its%206.3-inch%20display%2C%20the%20Pixel%209%20finished%20our%20intensive%20battery%20test%20with%2060%25%20remaining.%20That's%20right%20in%20line%20with%20other%20premium%20Android%20phones%20with%20similar%20display%20sizes%2C%20and%20it's%20more%20than%20adequate%20for%20most%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20practical%20terms%2C%20if%20you're%20using%20a%20similar-sized%20phone%2C%20the%20Pixel%209%20won't%20change%20your%20daily%20charging%20habits%2C%20as%20only%20larger%20phones%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20last%20longer%20than%20a%20typical%20day's%20use.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Pixel%209%20held%20in%20a%20hand%20against%20a%20tree%20bark%20background%2C%20focusing%20on%20the%20USB-C%20port%20on%20the%20bottome%20edge.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c8d1161aa2ac29ee33c997%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Pixel%209%20can%20charge%20up%20to%2027W%2C%20which%20is%20fine%2C%20but%20not%20especially%20impressive.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Pixel%209%20charges%20fairly%20rapidly%20at%2027W%2C%20and%20it's%20fine.%20I%20wish%20it%20charged%20at%20the%20same%2037W%20as%20the%20Pixel%209%20Pro%20XL%20(the%20Pixel%209%20Pro%20is%20also%2027W).%20The%20Pixel%209%20comes%20with%20a%20USB-C%20charging%20cable%20but%20no%20charger%20%E2%80%94%20just%20make%20sure%20your%20charger%20is%20capable%20of%2030W%20or%20more%20to%20get%20the%20fastest%20charging%20speed.%20The%20Pixel%209%20can%20also%20charge%20wirelessly%20up%20to%2015W%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhowl.me%2FcjLLeB0BvMn%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle's%202nd-gen%20Pixel%20Stand%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20it's%20compatible%20with%20standard%20Qi%20wireless%20chargers%20up%20to%2012W.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20comparing%20the%20Pixel%209's%20specs%20with%20the%20Pixel%209%20Pro%20models%2C%20you%20may%20notice%20the%20Pixel%209%20has%20a%2060-120Hz%20refresh%20rate%20display%20while%20the%20Pixel%209%20Pro%20models%20have%20variable%201-120Hz%20displays.%20Variable%20refresh%20rate%20displays%2C%20like%20those%20on%20the%20Pixel%209%20Pro%20models%2C%20are%20supposed%20to%20help%20improve%20battery%20life%20by%20reducing%20the%20refresh%20rate%20when%20the%20screen%20is%20static%2C%20as%20lower%20refresh%20rates%20usually%20reduce%20power%20drain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I%20found%20no%20tangible%20difference%20in%20battery%20drain%20from%20display%20refresh%20rates%20between%20the%20two%20phones.%20Both%20phones%20drained%20the%20same%204%25%20battery%20life%20over%20a%2012-hour%20test%20with%20the%20always-on%20display%20enabled%20compared%20to%20the%20same%20test%20with%20the%20option%20disabled.%20And%20there%20was%20no%20perceivable%20difference%20in%20battery%20life%20from%20using%20the%20phones%20normally.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cameras%5C%22%3ECameras%3A%20Superb%2C%20as%20usual%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Pixel%209%20has%20the%20same%2050MP%20main%20and%2048MP%20ultrawide%20cameras%20as%20the%20Pixel%209%20Pro%20models%2C%20so%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20upgrade%20to%20the%20high-end%20Pixel%20models%20to%20get%20one%20of%20the%20best%20phone%20cameras%20you%20can%20buy.%20It%20doesn't%20have%20a%20dedicated%20optical%20zoom%20lens%2C%20like%20the%205x%20camera%20on%20the%20Pixel%209%20Pro%20models%2C%20but%20the%20Pixel%209%20can%20take%20optical-quality%20photos%20at%202x%20zoom%20by%20cropping%20into%20its%20main%20camera%20sensor%2C%20and%20it%20still%20delivers%20high-quality%20images%20up%20to%205x%20zoom.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20has%20made%20a%20name%20for%20its%20Pixel%20cameras%2C%20which%20reliably%20take%20superb%20photos%20with%20balanced%20and%20natural-looking%20colors%2C%20along%20with%20superior%20lighting%20and%20contrast%20that%20create%20a%20better%20sense%20of%20depth%20than%20most%20other%20phone%20cameras.%20The%20Pixel%209%20keeps%20up%20the%20Pixel%20camera%20legacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20of%20a%20scenic%20lake%20landscape%20taken%20with%20the%20Pixel%209%20Pro%20XL's%20main%20camera.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c772cc1aa2ac29ee336761%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Pixel%209%20has%20the%20same%2050MP%20main%20camera%20as%20the%20Pixel%209%20Pro%20models.%20This%20photo%20was%20taken%20in%20the%20later%20afternoon%20in%20the%20Adirondack%20Mountains%20of%20upstate%20New%20York.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20of%20a%20scenic%20lake%20landscape%20taken%20with%20the%20Pixel%209%20Pro%20XL's%20ultrawide%20camera.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c7738c43b5e59d16b464d3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Pixel%209%20has%20the%20same%2048MP%20ultrawide%20camera%20as%20the%20Pixel%209%20Pro%20models.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20of%20a%20guide%20boat%20on%20a%20wooden%20dock%20on%20a%20lack%20taken%20with%20the%20Pixel%209%20Pro%20XL's%20main%20camera.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c774a043b5e59d16b4656e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Pixel%209%20takes%20beautiful%20photos.%20This%20photo%20was%20taken%20in%20the%20early%20morning%2C%20and%20a%20forest%20fire%20in%20Canada%20was%20causing%20the%20light%20to%20appear%20more%20orange%20than%20usual.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20of%20a%20guide%20boat%20on%20a%20wooden%20dock%20on%20a%20lack%20taken%20with%20the%20Pixel%209%20Pro%20XL's%20ultrawide%20camera.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c774cfc72ebc54a40e0997%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Pixel%209's%20upgraded%20ultrawide%20camera%20also%20produces%20fantastic%20results.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20taken%20inside%20a%20boathouse%20with%20several%20parked%20boats%20taken%20by%20the%20Pixel%209%20Pro%20XL's%20main%20camera.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c773dc1aa2ac29ee336857%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Pixel%209%20does%20an%20excellent%20job%20of%20balancing%20light%20and%20dark%20details.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2050MP%20main%20camera%20actually%20takes%2012MP%20photos%20by%20default%20%E2%80%94%20a%20result%20of%20combining%20four%20smaller%20pixels%20to%20form%20one%20larger%20pixel%2C%20otherwise%20known%20as%20pixel%20binning.%20You%20can%20take%2050MP%20photos%20if%20you%20want%2C%20but%20they'll%20take%20up%20way%20more%20space%20and%20superficially%20look%20the%20same%20as%2012MP%20photos.%20Only%20when%20you%20crop%20into%20a%2050MP%20photo%20will%20you%20see%20clearer%20details%20of%20objects%20and%20subjects%20that%20are%20further%20away.%20The%20default%2012MP%20option%20looks%20great%20for%20most%20people%2C%20but%20the%20Pixel%209's%20high-resolution%2050MP%20camera%20has%20other%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPixel%20binning%20also%20helps%20capture%20more%20light%2C%20which%20benefits%20low-light%20shots.%20It%20requires%20you%20to%20stay%20still%20for%20a%20few%20seconds%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20any%20faster%20than%20other%20top%20phones%20on%20the%20market%2C%20but%20the%20Pixel%209%20can%20take%20some%20great%20photos%20at%20night.%20If%20there's%20a%20bright%20light%20source%2C%20like%20a%20lightbulb%2C%20it%20does%20well%20to%20brighten%20up%20the%20areas%20that%20don't%20get%20the%20bulb's%20light%2C%20but%20not%20too%20aggressively%20to%20make%20it%20look%20like%20the%20scene%20is%20floodlit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20of%20a%20wooden%20balcony%20taken%20at%20night%20with%20the%20Pixel%209%20Pro%20XL's%20main%20camera.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c776281aa2ac29ee336a94%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Pixel%209%20takes%20excellent%20night%20shots.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20of%20a%20wood%20and%20stone%20building%20taken%20at%20night%20with%20the%20Pixel%209%20Pro%20XL's%20main%20camera.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c7764f43b5e59d16b466c7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Pixel%209%20handles%20darker%20parts%20in%20night%20shots%20very%20well%20without%20over-brightening.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20in%20extremely%20low%20light%20conditions%2C%20the%20Pixel%209%20can%20take%20photos%20that%20look%20good%20on%20the%20phone's%20display.%20However%2C%20you%20start%20to%20notice%20some%20pixelation%20and%20grainy%20artifacts%20when%20viewing%20ultra-low-light%20photos%20on%20a%20larger%20screen%2C%20like%20a%20computer%20monitor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20of%20a%20lake%20taken%20at%20night%20with%20the%20Pixel%209%20Pro%20XL's%20main%20camera.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c775ea1aa2ac29ee336a5b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShots%20taken%20by%20the%20Pixel%209%20in%20very%20low%20light%20conditions%20look%20fine%20on%20the%20phone's%20screen%2C%20but%20you%20can%20see%20some%20pixelation%20when%20viewing%20a%20larger%20version%20on%20a%20computer%20monitor.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Pixel%209%20supports%204K%20resolution%20up%20to%2060%20frames%20per%20second%20(fps)%2C%20and%20videos%20generally%20look%20great.%20There%20are%20some%20instances%20where%20brighter%20details%20in%20a%20bright%20environment%20become%20white%20and%20void%20of%20detail%2C%20but%20it's%20something%20that%20most%20phones%20struggle%20with.%20You%20can%20enable%2010-bit%20HDR%20to%20get%20even%20better%20colors%20and%20contrast%2C%20but%20make%20sure%20your%20monitor%20or%20TV%20supports%20HDR10%20if%20you%20plan%20on%20viewing%20your%20videos%20on%20those%20devices.%20If%20they%20don't%2C%20some%20videos%20can%20have%20incredibly%20unbalanced%20contrast%20and%20colors%20to%20the%20point%20of%20distraction.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20only%20complaint%20is%20that%20the%20Pixel%209's%20videos%20can%20appear%20somewhat%20choppy%20at%2030%20fps%20compared%20to%20comparable%20results%20from%20Apple's%20iPhones.%20You%20can%20get%20ultra-smooth%20videos%20using%20the%20Pixel%209's%2060%20fps%20option%2C%20but%20they%20use%20up%20a%20lot%20of%20storage%20space%20and%20give%20a%20soap%20opera%20look%20that's%20not%20for%20everyone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Gemini%20and%20AI%20features%5C%22%3EGemini%20and%20AI%20features%3A%20Powerful%2C%20generally%20useful%20tools%20with%20occasionally%20questionable%20results%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ai-gemini-bard%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGemini%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20assistant%20is%20basically%20a%20much%20smarter%2C%20more%20dynamic%20version%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fassistant.google.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Assistant%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20it's%20optional%20on%20the%20Pixel%209.%20Whether%20you're%20used%20to%20using%20Google%20Assistant%20or%20not%2C%20Gemini%20is%20worth%20a%20try%2C%20as%20it%20provides%20a%20novel%2C%20potentially%20more%20useful%20experience.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGemini%20still%20performs%20the%20same%20simpler%20tasks%20that%20Google%20Assistant%20historically%20has%2C%20like%20setting%20a%20timer%20or%20reminder%2C%20but%20it's%20generally%20much%20better%20at%20answering%20questions.%20It%20responds%20as%20if%20Gemini%2C%20the%20AI%20entity%2C%20is%20providing%20a%20comprehensive%20answer%20in%20straightforward%20language%20rather%20than%20pulling%20up%20a%20Google%20search%20and%20summarizing%20a%20single%20source%2C%20which%20is%20what%20Google%20Assistant%20mostly%20does.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20finding%20myself%20using%20Gemini%20more%20and%20more%20than%20performing%20a%20Google%20search%20manually.%20One%20of%20my%20favorite%20Gemini%20features%20is%20asking%20for%20%26quot%3Bkid-friendly%26quot%3B%20answers%20that%20explain%20things%20I%20don't%20fully%20understand%20faster%20than%20if%20I%20did%20the%20research%20myself%2C%20which%20is%20something%20Google%20Assistant%20doesn't%20do.%20However%2C%20I%20do%20wonder%20where%20Gemini%20is%20getting%20the%20information%20to%20answer%20my%20questions%20or%20requests%20at%20times%2C%20as%20sources%20sometimes%20aren't%20clearly%20cited%2C%20or%20cited%20at%20all.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20screenshots%20from%20the%20Pixel%209%20of%20Google's%20Gemini%20showing%20text%20answers%20to%20queries.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c8e075c72ebc54a40e7a3a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGoogle's%20Gemini%20AI%20assistant%20is%20an%20evolution%20of%20Google%20Assistant%2C%20and%20its%20results%20(pictured)%20are%20more%20comprehensive%20and%20potentially%20more%20useful.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Gemini%20assistant%20can%20also%20be%20inferior%20to%20Google%20Assistant%20in%20odd%20and%20specific%20ways.%20For%20example%2C%20Gemini%20refused%20to%20tell%20me%20anything%20about%20a%20political%20organization%20I%20wanted%20to%20learn%20more%20about.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Google%20Assistant%20pulled%20up%20and%20summarized%20the%20organization's%20Wikipedia%20entry%2C%20which%20is%20basically%20what%20I%20wanted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGemini%20can%20also%20be%20outright%20wrong%2C%20as%20shown%20in%20the%20screenshots%20below.%20When%20I%20asked%20whether%20the%20Pixel%209%20shares%20the%20same%20ultrawide%20camera%20as%20the%20Pixel%209%20Pro%2C%20Gemini%20told%20me%20it%20didn't.%20I%20double-checked%20with%20Google%2C%20and%20the%20Pixel%209%20does%2C%20indeed%2C%20have%20the%20same%2048MP%20ultrawide%20camera%20as%20the%20Pixel%209%20Pro.%20It's%20ironic%20Google's%20Gemini%20got%20information%20about%20Google's%20own%20phones%20so%20wrong.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20asking%20the%20time%20in%20a%20different%20time%20zone%20caused%20problems.%20I%20asked%20the%20time%20in%20Slovenia%2C%20and%20Gemini%20gave%20me%20the%20right%20time%20but%20the%20wrong%20%3Cem%3Etime%20of%20day%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20as%20it%20said%20the%20time%20was%20in%20a.m.%20when%20it%20was%20actually%20in%20p.m.%20When%20asked%20if%20the%20CET%20time%20zone%20was%20ahead%20or%20behind%20EDT%2C%20it%20wrongly%20stated%20it%20was%20behind.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20screenshots%20of%20the%20Gemini%20app%20showing%20answers%20to%20questions.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d751271d8d2deb96b84c24%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGemini%20struggled%20with%20a%20few%20fairly%20straightforward%20prompts.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20tap%20the%20Google%20symbol%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20an%20answer%20to%20help%20verify%20a%20Gemini%20answer%2C%20as%20it%20searches%20the%20web%20for%20results.%20Yet%2C%20the%20feature%20doesn't%20always%20work%3B%20pressing%20the%20symbol%20pointed%20out%20that%20Gemini's%20answer%20to%20the%20Pixel%209%20question%20may%20have%20been%20incorrect%2C%20but%20it%20pulled%20up%20irrelevant%20Google%20searches%20for%20the%20time%20zone%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Gemini's%20real%20power%20and%20usefulness%20become%20apparent%20when%20you%20start%20asking%20more%20complex%20things%2C%20like%20crafting%20an%20email%20outline%20to%20express%20a%20concern%20with%20an%20organization%2C%20finding%20fun%20things%20to%20do%20around%20a%20place%20you're%20visiting%2C%20coming%20up%20with%20ideas%20for%20an%20event%20(like%20a%20surprise%20birthday%20party)%2C%20and%20much%20more.%20It%20doesn't%20do%20the%20work%20for%20you%2C%20but%20it%20helps%20with%20the%20daunting%20%26quot%3Bwhere%20do%20I%20even%20start%3F%26quot%3B%20question.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20screenshots%20from%20the%20Pixel%209%20of%20Google's%20Gemini%20showing%20text%20answers%20to%20queries.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c8e1e443b5e59d16b4d36b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGemini%20can%20help%20get%20you%20started%20on%20things%20that%20might%20seem%20daunting%20or%20take%20time.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESwitching%20gears%20from%20Gemini%2C%20Google%20has%20built%20a%20comprehensive%20suite%20of%20software%20and%20AI-based%20camera%20and%20photo%20editing%20tools%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years.%20Magic%20Editor%2C%20Magic%20Eraser%2C%20and%20Best%20Take%20are%20some%20of%20the%20more%20useful%20and%20effective%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Pixel%209%2C%20Google%20is%20introducing%20Add%20Me%2C%20which%20lets%20a%20person%20taking%20a%20group%20photo%20be%20added%20to%20the%20photo.%20It%20works%20surprisingly%20well%20and%20is%20fairly%20easy%20to%20accomplish%2C%20especially%20after%20some%20practice.%20Results%20aren't%20always%20perfect%2C%20and%20small%20details%20can%20look%20out%20of%20place.%20Initial%20results%20can%20be%20pretty%20funny%20while%20you're%20learning%20to%20use%20Add%20Me%2C%20but%20photos%20were%20rarely%20ruined%20or%20unusable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20a%20Reimagine%20feature%20in%20Magic%20Editor%2C%20which%20lets%20you%20select%20parts%20of%20a%20photo%20and%20replace%20it%20with%20an%20AI-generated%20image.%20I'm%20trying%20to%20find%20a%20need%20to%2C%20say%2C%20change%20the%20background%20or%20setting%20a%20photo%20is%20taken%20in.%20I%20guess%20it%20can%20be%20for%20fun%3F%20Reimagine%20can%20create%20fairly%20decent%20scenery%2C%20but%20it's%20obviously%20fake.%20It%20also%20struggles%20deeply%20with%20recreating%20animals%20and%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20selfie%20of%20a%20man%20wearing%20a%20blue%20shirt%20taken%20with%20the%20Pixel%209%20Pro%20XL.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c7949a43b5e59d16b47685%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222736%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20original%20photo%20used%20to%20test%20Google's%20Reimagine%20feature.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20selfie%20of%20a%20man%20wearing%20a%20blue%20shirt%20with%20the%20background%20changed%20to%20a%20tropical%20beach%20using%20Google's%20AI%20Reimagine%20feature%20on%20the%20Pixel%209%20Pro%20XL.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c794ccc72ebc54a40e1c13%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222736%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20told%20Reimagine%20to%20replace%20the%20background%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Btropical%20beach%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20it%20did%20OK.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20of%20a%20man%20in%20a%20blue%20shirt%20with%20the%20background%20changed%20to%20a%20pack%20of%20wolves%20using%20Google's%20Reimagine%20AI%20feature%20on%20the%20Pixel%209%20Pro%20XL.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c794fb43b5e59d16b476e8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222736%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20then%20asked%20it%20to%20replace%20the%20background%20with%20a%20pack%20of%20wolves%2C%20but%20AI%20does%20a%20terrible%20job%20of%20recreating%20animals.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20the%20new%20Screenshots%20app%2C%20which%20acts%20like%20a%20Google%20Photos%20search%20specifically%20for%20screenshots%20you've%20taken%20to%20remind%20you%20of%20something.%20I've%20used%20it%20similarly%20to%20how%20I%20use%20Shazam%3A%20to%20recognize%20a%20song%20and%20keep%20it%20in%20my%20Shazam%20library%20to%20return%20to%20later.%20I've%20never%20used%20screenshots%20to%20remind%20me%20of%20something%20for%20later%2C%20but%20Screenshots%20is%20changing%20that.%20It's%20not%20totally%20effective%2C%20as%20it%20can%20miss%20some%20screenshots%20and%20add%20some%20that%20are%20entirely%20irrelevant%20to%20my%20search.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20taken%20from%20the%20Pixel%209%20running%20Google's%20Screenshots%20app%20showing%20screenshots%20relevant%20to%20the%20search%20term%20%26quot%3Bmovies.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ccad461aa2ac29ee3428c2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Screenshots%20app%20was%20able%20to%20find%20most%20of%20the%20screenshots%20I%20took%20to%20remind%20myself%20of%20movies%20I%20want%20to%20see%20later%2C%20but%20not%20all%20of%20them%2C%20and%20it%20included%20a%20completely%20irrelevant%20screenshot.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FB