%20shows%20the%20infant%20in%20a%20yellow%20plastic%20crate%20placed%20on%20a%20foam%20board%20as%20the%20men%20trudged%20through%20the%20muddy%20waters%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh's%20Vijaywada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20had%20to%20move%20the%20baby%20out%20of%20their%20house%20as%20the%20floodwaters%20turned%20roads%20into%20rivers%20and%20waterlogged%20homes%20in%20the%20Singh%20Nagar%20locality%20like%20almost%20every%20other%20area%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20video%20showed%20more%20than%20200%20cars%20-%20many%20of%20them%20luxury%20SUVs-%20submerged%20in%20the%20floodwaters%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20Tuesday%2C%20323%20trains%20were%20cancelled%20in%20Vijayawada%2C%20170%20diverted%20and%2012%20partially%20cancelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20torrential%20floods%20have%20killed%2027%20people%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana%20and%20damaged%20properties%20with%20lakhs%20rescued%20and%20taken%20to%20relief%20camps.%20Many%20industries%20have%20also%20suffered%20massive%20losses%20due%20to%20the%20heavy%20rains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Air%20Forces%20has%20flown%20in%20hundreds%20of%20rescue%20officers%20and%20tonnes%20of%20emergency%20aid%20to%20both%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERains%20cause%20widespread%20destruction%20every%20year%2C%20but%20experts%20say%20climate%20change%20is%20shifting%20weather%20patterns%20and%20increasing%20the%20number%20of%20extreme%20weather%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAndhra%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20said%20he%20was%20undertaking%20surprise%20inspections%20in%20the%20flood-affected%20areas%20and%20directly%20taking%20feedback%20from%20the%20people%20through%20the%20Interactive%20Voice%20Response%20System%20(IVRS)%20mode.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20undergoing%20hardships.%20Snakes%20and%20scorpions%20are%20even%20entering%20upper%20floor%20residences.%20I%20am%20conducting%20IVRS%20and%20receiving%20information%20that%20food%20is%20not%20reaching%20some%20places.%20Rise%20up%20to%20the%20occasion%20and%20work%20with%20humanity%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Naidu.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725384060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Foml2qs9g_baby-in-crate_625x300_03_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fandhra-pradesh-news%2Fandhra-pradesh-floods-baby-in-plastic-crate-carried-by-men-in-andhra-flood-waters-6483939%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20men%20wading%20through%20neck-deep%20water%2C%20carrying%20a%20baby%20in%20a%20plastic%20crate%20-%20this%20was%20one%20of%20the%20scores%20of%20distressing%20scenes%20inflicted%20by%20the%20deluge%20in%20the%20southern%20states%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fandhra-pradesh-news%2Fandhra-pradesh-floods-baby-in-plastic-crate-carried-by-men-in-andhra-flood-waters-6483939%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IT%20hiring%20declines%20in%20August%2C%20but%20AI-ML%20jobs%20outlier%20with%2014%25%20rise%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725383684000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-10%2F22%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1697997290-1732.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Foverall-hiring-declines-in-august-ai-ml-jobs-see-14-growth-report-124090301122_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20overall%20white-collar%20hiring%20activity%20during%20the%20month%20witnessed%20a%20dip%20of%203%25%20on%20a%20yearly%20basis%20in%20August%20this%20year%2C%20said%20the%20report%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Foverall-hiring-declines-in-august-ai-ml-jobs-see-14-growth-report-124