ations%2C%20explains%20Harssh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20AI%20can%20process%20and%20analyse%20data%20at%20scales%20beyond%20human%20capability%2C%20the%20technology%20is%20still%20in%20its%20early%20stages.%20The%20more%20data%20AI%20algorithms%20are%20exposed%20to%2C%20the%20more%20refined%20and%20accurate%20they%20become%2C%20just%20like%20Raven%20Sentry%20proved.%20Initially%2C%20while%20the%20predictions%20weren%E2%80%99t%20correct%2C%20as%20and%20when%20the%20data%20increased%2C%20it%20predicted%20an%20attack%20in%20Jalalabad%2C%20Afghanistan%2C%20which%20occurred%20a%20few%20days%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMARVEL%E2%80%99s%20long-term%20goal%20is%20to%20perfect%20these%20algorithms%20over%20time%2C%20ensuring%20that%20they%20can%20eventually%20provide%20near-flawless%20support%20to%20law%20enforcement%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20technology%20continues%20to%20evolve%2C%20MARVEL%E2%80%99s%20work%20today%20is%20setting%20the%20stage%20for%20a%20future%20where%20AI%20and%20human%20expertise%20work%20hand%20in%20hand%20to%20maintain%20law%20and%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESources%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.economist.com%2Fscience-and-technology%2F2024%2F07%2F31%2Fhow-america-built-an-ai-tool-to-predict-taliban-attacks%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98How%20America%20built%20an%20AI%20tool%20to%20predict%20Taliban%20attacks%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fa%3EPublished%20on%2031%20July%202024%2C%20Courtesy%20The%20Economist%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724680016000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FIMG-20240826-WA0073-1724677884.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D362886%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Maharashtra%20government's%20MARVEL%20will%20augment%20law%20enforcement%20by%20developing%20AI%20tools%2